    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Be prepared for any situation with the ASR Outdoor Drop Point Pocket Knife! This pocket knife features a thumb assist drop point blade constructed of durable steel. The handle has a comfortable ergonomic grip to prevent slippage during use, and the handle has a cool black wood inlay. The knife unfolds to an overall length of 8&quot;, the blade itself is 3.5&quot; and it folds to a compact 4.5&quot;. The knife also has a metal pocket clip that allows you to easily secure the blade when not in use. This is a great every day carry tool or gift idea for knife collectors and outdoor enthusiasts.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor Styled Inlay Pocket Knife Steel Blade Thumb Assist Open Pocket Clip</h2>\n  <p>Be prepared for any situation with the ASR Outdoor Drop Point Pocket Knife!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>DURABLE CONSTRUCTION - CR13 Steel Wont Rust | Cool Black Wood Inlay Design | Easy Thumb Assist Open</li>\n    <li>DROP POINT BLADE - DROP POINT BLADE - Convex Spine for Easily Controlled Point &amp; Big Belly for Slicing | Great Blade for Hunters</li>\n    <li>POCKET CLIP - Sturdy Clip Attached for Easy Storage When Not In Use | Keeps Blade Secured</li>\n    <li>ERGONOMIC HANDLE - Thumb Assist Open &amp; Comfortable Grip Prevents Slippage During Use</li>\n    <li>COMPACT DESIGN- 8&quot; Overall Length, 3.5&quot; Blade, 4.5&quot; Folded | Fits Easily Inside Pocket, Bag or Backpack</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/tools/folding_knives/PBK203BK_pocketknife_main.jpg\" alt=\"Be prepared for any situation with the ASR Outdoor Drop Point Pocket Knife\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> ASROWPKBLK</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 060886928812</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> 8 in</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>This pocket knife features a thumb assist drop point blade constructed of durable steel. The handle has a comfortable ergonomic grip to prevent slippage during use, and the handle has a cool black wood inlay. The knife unfolds to an overall length of 8&quot;, the blade itself is 3.5&quot; and it folds to a compact 4.5&quot;.</p>\n  <p>The knife also has a metal pocket clip that allows you to easily secure the blade when not in use. This is a great every day carry tool or gift idea for knife collectors and outdoor enthusiasts.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
